<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
	<title>OTP Verification</title>
	<style>
		.container {
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			max-width: 400px;
			margin: auto;
			padding: 20px;
			border: 1px solid #ddd;
			border-radius: 8px;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.otp {
			font-size: 24px;
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #333;
		}

		.footer {
			font-size: 12px;
			color: #777;
			margin-top: 20px;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
		<h2>Your OTP Code</h2>
		<p>Use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification:</p>
		<p class="otp">{{otp}}</p>
		<p>This OTP will expire in 5 minutes.</p>
		<div class="footer">If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</div>
	</div>
</body>

</html>
